        "dsc": {
            "value": "\u003cc id=\"aspace_ref11\" level=\"series\"\u003e\u003cdid\u003e\u003cunittitle\u003eSeries I: National Office\u003c/unittitle\u003e\u003cunitdate\u003e1935-1980\u003c/unitdate\u003e\u003c/did\u003e\u003carrangement id=\"aspace_2317f67afb0e1d067445498ca7ab2562\"\u003e\u003chead\u003eArrangement\u003c/head\u003e\u003cp\u003eArranged chronologically.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/arrangement\u003e\u003cscopecontent id=\"aspace_07d90138d40f43e1506fef9da9db07a2\"\u003e\u003chead\u003eScope and Content Note\u003c/head\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis series contains materials generated by the main office of the American Committee for Protection of Foreign Born from 1935-1980. The types of materials contained in this series include leaflets, articles, writings, correspondence, convention materials, circulars, press releases, and other ephemeral materials. Topics in the files include Nazi Germany, the Walter-McCarran Immigration Bill, Subversive Activities Control Board, deportation trials, and Haitian refugees.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/scopecontent\u003e\u003cc id=\"aspace_ref12\" level=\"file\"\u003e\u003cdid\u003e\u003cunittitle\u003eAmerican Committee for Protection of Foreign Born\u003c/unittitle\u003e\u003cunitdate normal=\"1935/1949\" type=\"inclusive\"\u003e1935-1949\u003c/unitdate\u003e\u003ccontainer id=\"aspace_490613edf4b524692e41dd5404510ce5\" label=\"Mixed Materials\" type=\"Box\"\u003e1\u003c/container\u003e\u003ccontainer parent=\"aspace_490613edf4b524692e41dd5404510ce5\" type=\"Folder\"\u003e1\u003c/container\u003e\u003c/did\u003e\u003c/c\u003e\u003cc id=\"aspace_ref13\" level=\"file\"\u003e\u003cdid\u003e\u003cunittitle\u003eAmerican Committee for Protection of Foreign Born\u003c/unittitle\u003e\u003cunitdate normal=\"1951/1954\" type=\"inclusive\"\u003e1951-1954\u003c/unitdate\u003e\u003ccontainer id=\"aspace_b8f785c53dc3e3f697a752306c36fa0e\" label=\"Mixed Materials\" type=\"Box\"\u003e1\u003c/container\u003e\u003ccontainer parent=\"aspace_b8f785c53dc3e3f